data.description:
Sellers are very motivated !!! Bring all offers.....Seller will offer 5k in closing cost with acceptable 

Charming two bedroom one bath bungalow in the serene countryside with a tree lined lot.  This home boast LVP floors in all but one room.  All the rooms are very spacious.  When you enter the home from the back, you can enter from the back deck or from the mud room.  The mud room has tons of storage.  Enjoy lovely evening or barbeques out on the covered back deck or the covered front porch. Custom closets have been installed in both closets.  Decorative beams were added to the living room ceiling for charm by the previous owner.  Situated on over 1 acre this home offers a great blend of comfort and country living. Sellers are leaving the front load washer and dryer with the home. The driveway offers tons of parking.  

*****Beginning of driveway is shared with neighbor but has never been an issue****
